data.description: Nice 3 bedrooms and 2 Full baths home with a split master floor plan. Previously Dryden Enterprises built "Caitlin" floor plan. This property has a formal dining plus a kitchen with an Island. Located in a great growing neighborhood. Projected to have shopping center at front entrance of the Community. Really close to shopping, dining, and recreation. Located just a few miles from Front gate of Fort Stewart. Property Sold "AS IS!!!"
